<span style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;">**<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">First of all, life in North Korea is very, very bad… </span>**</span>
<span style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;">**<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Tom Head, </span>**accessed 9/27/**<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">10</span>**, “Human Rights in North Korea - North Korean <span style="font-size: 8pt;">Human Rights Abuses” http://civilliberty.about.com/od/international humanrights/p/northkorea101.htm</span></span>
