<span style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;">Doug <span class="cite">**Bandow**</span>, **<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">1998</span>**, senior fellow @ CATO, 11-11-<span class="cite"><span style="font-weight: normal;">2008</span></span>, “Seoul Searching,” http://www.nationalinterest.org/Article.aspx?id=20218</span>
